{"tid":752013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[今晚又食自己]雜菌鮮蝦飯","createTime":"2018-07-22T12:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T12:48:04.000Z","uid":57555,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28868106fc854bd64067939fca8b859725fdd783","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/200635_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F200635_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg&h=8120e779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說老母去左玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚我煮比老豆細妹食<br />\n其實個做法有D似燉飯<br />\n不過我又唔敢叫佢雜菌鮮蝦「燉」飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一黎係用珍珠米<br />\n二黎唔係生米炒到熟<br />\n不過個煮法都有D似"},{"pid":"117ccd8faf980fd82cbe293b82725ee5c97f2563","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/201228_cb7c6443ebd24f4c73a1abf135c5b111.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F201228_cb7c6443ebd24f4c73a1abf135c5b111.jpeg&h=47891cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主要材料有:<br />\n蝦................1斤<br />\n雜菌............適量<br />\n洋蔥............半個<br />\n珍珠米.........2嘜<br />\n蒜頭.............6瓣<br />\n牛奶.............100ml"},{"pid":"9863a71fa208d7ce235fb4793d64f2f245211fb7","tid":752013,"uid":132993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28868106fc854bd64067939fca8b859725fdd783","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/200635_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F200635_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg&h=8120e779&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說老母去左玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚我煮比老豆細妹食<br />\n其實個做法有D似燉飯<br />\n不過我又唔敢叫佢雜菌鮮蝦「燉」飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為一黎係用珍珠米<br />\n二黎唔係生米炒到熟<br />\n不過個煮法都有D似"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:15:41.000Z","msg":"求做法"},{"pid":"4681077a024fcafb2c29cf77e37f459e44e9e122","tid":752013,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"哎喲不錯哦"},{"pid":"097293d705d5a0f3ee7b57e0a7c4c12edfd98f91","tid":752013,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:17:36.000Z","msg":"可否請我食少少 please"},{"pid":"102a15f9d776ac0fffb69c5d2184ec892aaa5512","tid":752013,"uid":81164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"Why not 洋蔥？"},{"pid":"e1326642df4bea8f6ef8e8fb73f9c052586fc1c5","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/201747_2249927950e9531687c6b27ed96ffc36.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F201747_2249927950e9531687c6b27ed96ffc36.jpeg&h=73d658ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一樣野先剝蝦殼<br />\n剝之前最好正佢幾個鐘<br />\n會易D剝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/201939_7904c1d09e331f6ee4cca5736d26ff65.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F201939_7904c1d09e331f6ee4cca5736d26ff65.jpeg&h=6aca5d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後比D油落鑊<br />\n開大火爆香佢"},{"pid":"e9fe92aa85b2bd9bf90529c16c1f9682cd8644b0","tid":752013,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"f331e6a55b12fb674f01c1da7f414f84e025283b","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"爆完用鑊鉦鏟鋤爆D蝦頭<br />\n再加水至蓋過蝦殼<br />\n煲佢4個字左右<br />\n之後隔走D蝦殼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/202226_f85dbe57fac1d2f82b6be7dbccc0bdf7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F202226_f85dbe57fac1d2f82b6be7dbccc0bdf7.jpeg&h=fda2f881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n偷飲左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢兜湯已經好好味"},{"pid":"15e7b3b973cf5936fe257f5d5a61edb625ba1a02","tid":752013,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"屋企徐晃幾大？<br />\n貢大個鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843330cbc865acf2d8cc7268523015ffe2425f1b","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/202443_f72f40eefa1408968a110511723ebfb5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F202443_f72f40eefa1408968a110511723ebfb5.jpeg&h=719252fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煲湯期間<br />\n可以備料先"},{"pid":"2c21ea1b30977778b9b70060e1693e6c26e9993a","tid":752013,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"見到都唔想食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1f7e50f96e29add29055a7eb8637082a9c67cf","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/203002_73193f70e532a02e0b1c5cb27142bb44.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F203002_73193f70e532a02e0b1c5cb27142bb44.jpeg&h=64a77303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炸起D蒜片備用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/203049_8712985e23ec1e666197c8822910be04.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F203049_8712985e23ec1e666197c8822910be04.jpeg&h=8ca6df1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留番少量蒜油大火炒香D菇<br />\n唔洗成日反仍<br />\n比D時間佢上色"},{"pid":"74899e9d2efe0c4bdde953bbc660afe57cf0740f","tid":752013,"uid":46835,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed837b3212dbf8253bf2c47d66eb24aa71aa2b2","tid":752013,"uid":137487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6feb108f4559209f575ffeea687c59a5d1f76d1","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/203237_0e86e42f735a6cc7c8f6a2fb2464e35d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F203237_0e86e42f735a6cc7c8f6a2fb2464e35d.jpeg&h=5ee47c77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煎蝦前爆爆D洋蔥<br />\n唔記得左影影<br />\n<br />\nD蝦比少少鹽、黑椒撈撈佢<br />\n大火煎<br />\n蝦最後煎，因為煎完隻PAN會比較污糟"},{"pid":"36c38eb9147f001acbe5c147521926aaf501d312","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/203502_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F203502_728cc7d4f6a28872570df7dd5ecb40b7.jpg&h=fba2c605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煮果陣冇影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗洗PAN<br />\n直落飯(之前已經煲定)、洋蔥、菇<br />\n落一半湯，中火兜勻佢<br />\n收乾就再落埋淨番D湯<br />\n落100ml牛奶再兜<br />\n順手落鹽同黑椒調味<br />\n熄火落20g牛油撈勻<br />\n蝦同蒜片鋪面就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795c73543f9418f7bf78018235246987e205c28e","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"SORRY<br />\n賣相唔係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed536ffe8cb3b7c14e8fddadd6694d735fbfa6c","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"102a15f9d776ac0fffb69c5d2184ec892aaa5512","tid":752013,"uid":81164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"Why not 洋蔥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"有落呀"},{"pid":"3fba6ddd16570ddab5e3d81fe65faaf40ba67ea2","tid":752013,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d644062c45029d21543799c5956664febe4718","tid":752013,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"開錯左台<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/752046/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/752046/page/1</a>"}]}